Telkom has launched its Big Deal for July 2018. The company has two uncapped LTE deals for users this month, which are: Telkom said that for the “Business Hours” package, users will receive uncapped LTE services between midnight and 17:00 each day. The “All Hours” package provides users with uncapped LTE for 24 hours a day. Telkom has stated that the uncapped LTE packages are subject to a fair usage policy, but the terms and conditions of the deals were not available at the time of writing. Both deals include a Huawei B525 router, which can handle four LAN-connected devices, and 64 wireless devices at a time. A voice service – with a flat rate of 70c to all networks, and 300 on-net voice minutes – is also included. The packages are available until 31 July 2018, or while stocks last. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>